examples:
  - special operations operator ignoring peripheral pain to complete mission objective
  - predictive brain suppressing prediction errors to maintain motor control
  - AI agent deprioritizing low-urgency alerts during critical execution window
  - submarine crew sealing flooded compartment to preserve vessel function

